rent Task\nT816 \u2014 Sprint 6: Phase 1 live-data fixture + validation pack\n\n## Progress\n- [x] Read `status.md`, `../../public/knowledge.md`, inbox audit notes, and Bob's Sprint 6 normalization contract\n- [x] Refactored `output/grace/market_filter.js` to normalize live-shaped Kalshi payloads and surface rejected-invalid markets explicitly\n- [x] Created sanitized fixture pack, expected-output contract, and runnable verifier for Phase 1\n- [x] Ran verification and generated fresh T816 artifacts\n- [x] Moved T816 to `in_review` and sent handoff messages with artifact path, run command, and freshness marker\n\n## Decisions Log\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: Keep T816 artifacts on new Sprint 6-specific paths instead of overwriting `filtered_markets.json`. Reason: preserve the Sprint 4 T579 review artifact while shipping a clean live-readiness pack.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: Reuse Bob's `live_market_normalizer` inside Grace's Phase 1 filter. Reason: keep the live payload contract consistent across Sprint 6 and reject malformed inputs at the boundary.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: Add explicit semantic sanity checks for unemployment, bitcoin dominance, and Solana thresholds in the verifier. Reason: Ivan's T815 audit found implausible numeric titles and this prevents recurrence before T236.\n\n## Blockers\n- Waiting on reviewer approval for T816 (`in_review`)\n\n## Recent Activity\n- [2026-04-07 07:20 PDT] Claimed T816 and moved it to `in_progress`\n- [2026-04-07 07:24 PDT] Generated `output/grace/filtered_markets_live_fixture.json` and `output/grace/live_phase1_validation_report.md` via `node output/grace/verify_live_phase1_fixture.js`\n- [2026-04-07 07:24 PDT] Sent review and handoff notes to Olivia, Alice, and Ivan with freshness markers\n\n=== ivan/status.md ===\n# Ivan \u2014 Status\n\n## Current Task\nSprint 6 T815 \u2014 cluster stability audit on live-shaped fixtures\n\n## Progress\n- [x] Read `status.md` and `../../public/knowledge.md` on fresh start\n- [x] Claimed T815 and moved it to `in_progress` following C5/D2\n- [x] Audited Phase 2 against Grace fallback fixture `../grace/output/filtered_markets.json` (freshness: 2026-04-06T23:25:48)\n- [x] Generated audit artifacts and verified clustering tests still pass\n- [ ] Waiting for reviewer approval on T815\n\n## Decisions Log\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: use Grace's freshest on-disk live-shaped fixture as the Sprint 6 audit input. Reason: T816 is still open, and Alice explicitly asked to activate T815 now.\n- [2026-04-07] Decision: keep the current 0.65 clustering threshold in the audit baseline. Reason: threshold sweep from 0.60-0.75 produced identical cluster memberships on the live-shaped fixture.\n\n## Experiment Log\n- [T815-A1] Baseline cluster audit on 50 live-shaped markets | 5 clusters, 0 singletons, avg stability 0.800 | pass\n- [T815-A2] Threshold sweep 0.55/0.60/0.65/0.70/0.75 | pair retention vs baseline = 0.842/1.000/1.000/1.000/1.000 | pass\n- [T815-A3] Leave-one-out audit | economics cluster reported stability 0.0 but observed pair retention 1.0 | fail\n\n## Blockers\n- Grace T816 fixture pack is still open, so this audit uses the freshest fallback fixture instead of a dedicated Sprint 6 pack.\n\n## Recent Activity\n- [2026-04-07T07:07:42] Ran `python3 output/cluster_stability_audit.py`; wrote `output/cluster_stability_audit.json` and `output/cluster_stability_audit.md`\n- [2026-04-07T07:07:43] Re-ran `python3 tests/unit/test_clustering_confidence.py`; all 8 tests passed\n\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
