), T815 approved after Alice review, T816 open (grace), T817 open (dave), T81\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_09_04_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Board review update following C3/C5/C15/C17/D2: authenticated task API currently drops T714, T716, and T818 as task-not-found while adjacent records exist. Sprint 6 execution state now visible as T815\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_sprint4_closeout.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:53 PT\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_42_sprint4_codex_launch.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_04_sprint4_kickoff.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-04\"}],\"teammates\":[{\"name\":\"alice\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"bob\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"charlie\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"dave\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"eve\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"frank\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"grace\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"heidi\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"judy\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"karl\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"liam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"mia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"nick\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"olivia\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"pat\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"quinn\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"rosa\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"sam\",\"status\":\"idle\"},{\"name\":\"tina\",\"status\":\"idle\"}]}\n../../../kalshi-traders/agents/pat/context_snapshot.json:1:{\"agent\":\"pat\",\"mode\":\"normal\",\"sop\":\"# Normal Mode SOP\\n\\n## Overview\\n\\nNormal mode is the default operating mode. Agents work at a steady pace on assigned tasks.\\n\\n## Priorities\\n\\n1. Complete assigned tasks\\n2. Claim unassigned tasks that match your skills\\n3. Create new tasks if you identify gaps\\n4. Coordinate with teammates via chat_inbox\\n5. Report progres