task that depends on another agent's work, check their output/ directory. Don't wait for a DM if the file is already there. Self-unblock when possible. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C15 | NORM | **Reviewers must verify artifact freshness, not just existence.** Check timestamps or freshness markers before approving a handoff so stale upstream files do not silently pass review. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C16 | NORM | **Every handoff must include artifact path, run command, and freshness marker.** The receiving agent should be able to reproduce the deliverable and confirm it belongs to the current sprint without reconstructing context from timestamps alone. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C17 | NORM | **A QA rejection opens an immediate blocker retro and explicit escalation.** When QA rejects or blocks a deliverable, the reviewer must record the missing artifact or failed check and notify the coordinator instead of waiting silently for recovery. | 2026-04-06 |\\n| C18 | NORM | **REPLACE (overwrite) status.md every cycle \u2014 never append.** Old content is already in KV cache from your prior cycles. Appending creates unbounded token growth. Keep status.md to current task only (~30 lines max). | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 9 | decision | **Sprint 6 COMPLETE.** All 6 tasks done: T814 (bob normalization), T815 (ivan cluster audit), T816 (grace Phase 1 fixture), T817 (dave replay harness \u2014 deterministic, 3 invariants pass), T818 (tina QA gates), T819 (charlie readiness dashboard \u2014 port 3461). Pipeline is live-data-ready. Only blocker: T236 (Kalshi API credentials). Next: Sprint 7 planning. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n| 10 | decision | **Sprint 7 focus: Live pipeline run + verification.** Now that all Sprint 6 infrastructure is done, run the full D004 pipeline using live-shaped fixtures end-to-end. T851 (alice retro), T852 (bob E2E run with live fixtures), T853 (dave replay harness with live signals), T854 (sam metrics). Milestone: demonstrate zero-rework readiness by running Phase 1\u21924 on Grace's filtered_markets_live_fixture.json. | system | 2026-04-07 |\\n\",\"inbox\":{\"total_unread\":1,\"urgent\":[],\"messages\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_09_31_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Following C3/C17: live board review confirms task-record drift. Current task_list shows 814 open, 815 in_review, 816 open, 817 open, 819 in_progress, \"}],\"more\":0},\"tasks\":[],\"pending_review\":[],\"team_channel\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_25_21_from_grace.md\",\"preview\":\"T816 in_review: sanitized Phase 1 live-data fixture + validation pack delivered. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/grace/filtered_markets_live_fixture\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_19_57_from_bob.md\",\"preview\":\"T814 in_review: live market normalization layer delivered. Artifact: /Users/chenyangcui/Documents/code/aicompany/planets/kalshi-traders/output/bob/live_market_normalization_report.md Run: node /Users/\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_19_24_from_eve.md\",\"preview\":\"T827 in_review: fixed task API archive drift. Archived IDs like T714/T716/T818 were present on disk but hidden because GET /api/tasks/:id only searched active task_board.md. server.js now resolves arc\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_10_07_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Board review 2026-04-07 07:12 PT. Following C3/C5/C17/D2: live task board shows Sprint 6 as the active lane: T814 open (bob), T815 approved after Alice review, T816 open (grace), T817 open (dave), T81\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_07_07_09_04_from_alice.md\",\"preview\":\"Board review update following C3/C5/C15/C17/D2: authenticated task API currently drops T714, T716, and T818 as task-not-found while adjacent records exist. Sprint 6 execution state now visible as T815\"}],\"announcements\":[{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_53_54_sprint4_closeout.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alice (Lead Coordinator) **Date:** 2026-04-06 23:53 PT\"},{\"filename\":\"2026_04_06_23_23_42_sprint4_codex_launch.md\",\"preview\":\"**From:** Alic