{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_30", "type": "command_execution", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"rg -n \\\"\\\\| 817 \\\\||\\\\| 819 \\\\|\\\" ../../../kalshi-traders/shared/task_board_archive.md\"", "aggregated_output": "437:| 817 | Sprint 6: Deterministic replay harness for risk controls | Following D5/C8: build a replayable execution-path harness that proves stop-loss, capital floor, and order-path behavior against deterministic signal fixtures. Deliver artifact path, run command, freshness marker, and evidence suitable for Tina QA. | high | all | dave | done | 2026-04-07 | 2026-04-07 | [2026-04-07] Activating T817: reviewing replay-harness requirements and current execution path. ;; [2026-04-07] [2026-04-07] Dave: replay_report.json delivered \u2014 3 scenarios (baseline, tiny_cap, capital_floor_halt), all deterministic (canonical hashes recorded). Ready for Tina/Olivia review. ;; [2026-04-07] [REVIEWED by olivia] Replay harness verified: 3 scenarios (baseline, tiny_cap, capital_floor_halt), all deterministic. Canonical hashes recorded. assertScenarioInvariants passes. Minor: expected counts in baseline/tiny_cap differ from observed (mock data generates 1 signal, not 2) \u2014 cosmetic only, invariants are correct. \u2014 deliverable: agents/dave/output/ ;; [2026-04-07] [REVIEWED by olivia] Verified: deterministic harness, 3 scenarios pass \u2014 deliverable: agents/dave/output/ |\n438:| 819 | Sprint 6: Readiness dashboard for artifacts, blockers, and run commands | Following D005/C10: publish a lightweight dashboard or report view that surfaces Sprint 6 artifact locations, blocker state, and runnable commands so coordination stays visible while we wait on T236. | medium | all | charlie | done | 2026-04-07 | 2026-04-07 | [2026-04-07] Activated T819 and started dashboard implementation ;; [2026-04-07] Resumed T819; auditing existing dashboard patterns and Sprint 6 artifacts to build readiness view with artifact paths, blocker state, and run commands. ;; [2026-04-07] [2026-04-07] Charlie: sprint6_readiness_dashboard.html + serve_sprint6_readiness_dashboard.js on port 3461. Shows 4 done artifacts (T814, T815, T816, T818). Ready for review. ;; [2026-04-07] [REVIEWED by olivia] Readiness dashboard verified: port 3461, /api/readiness shows 5 ready artifacts (T814-T818), T817+T819 in_review. T236 blocker correctly flagged. Fixed artifact path for T816 (filtered_markets_live_fixture.json). Dashboard is production-ready. \u2014 deliverable: agents/charlie/output/ ;; [2026-04-07] [REVIEWED by olivia] Verified: dashboard running on port 3461, 5 artifacts ready \u2014 deliverable: agents/charlie/output/ |\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
