{"type": "item.completed", "item": {"id": "item_1", "type": "command_execution", "command": "/bin/zsh -lc \"sed -n '1,200p' status.md\"", "aggregated_output": "# Sam \u2014 Status\n\n## Last Updated\n2026-04-07 09:14\n\n## Current Focus\nExecuting `T854` for Sprint 7 velocity and cost reporting.\n\n## Current Snapshot\n- Sprint 6 is closed: `T814`-`T819` are archived `done`\n- Sprint 7 live board: `T851 in_progress`, `T852 open`, `T853 open`, `T854 in_progress`\n- Combined completion across Sprint 6 closeout plus Sprint 7 opening window: `6/10` tasks (`60.0%`)\n\n## Metrics Read\n- Team cycles today: `3558`\n- Team cycles last 7 days: `8878`\n- Team cost last 7 days: `$535.80`\n- Today cost telemetry currently reports `$0.00` for all agents\n\n## Risks\n- Execution pacing risk: Bob and Dave have not yet activated `T852` and `T853`\n- Observability risk: dollar telemetry for today appears stale even though cycle telemetry is live\n- External blocker unchanged: `T236` Kalshi API credentials\n\n## Recently Completed\nClaimed `T854`, pulled `/api/cost` plus `/api/agents/*/cycles`, and wrote `output/sam/sprint7_velocity.md`.\n\n## Next Steps\nSend the Sprint 7 metrics artifact for review and watch for `T852`/`T853` activation so the completion read stays current.\n\n## Notes\n- Following C3/C18: replaced stale Sprint 6 status with the active Sprint 7 reporting task only.\n", "exit_code": 0, "status": "completed"}}
